high_descs: Turn around and go around the table and into the adjoining living room. Stop in front of the glass coffee table.
Turn around and head across the room to the white safe on the floor in the corner behind the black desk.
Put the blue vase into the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put the blue vase into the safe.

high_descs: Turn to the left, and go around the back side of the table to the right. Turn left to go in the living room, go the left around the glass coffee table and then right again to face it.
Pick up the blue vase from the table.
Turn right and then left to go around the table. Turn left and find the small box in the far corner of the room.
Open the small box, place the vase inside and shut it again.
anns.task_desc: Place the blue vase in the safe on the floor.

high_descs: Turn around, and then go right at the table; exit the room and go straight to the coffee table, then go left, then right to stop at the coffee table.
Pick up the vase on the right side of the table.
Turn right, then left, then right toward the doorway, then turn left to go around the desk.
Put the vase in the safe to the right of the desk, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a vase in a safe.
